{
  "stem": "27285.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were a whole train of children and survivors who went via-- via Paris.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was also a story-- via Paris to Haifa and-- I mean, to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We got--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was legal, completely legal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] repatriate whatever train.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went onto Marseilles, and from Marseilles to Paris-- or it'd be different now from-- I don't know which way you go first.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, from Marseilles you shipped [INAUDIBLE] to Haifa. yes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was of course, no plane over there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It took quite some time, and--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she put you-- saw you onto the train?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She put me onto the train, yes, and I was very cross with her.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Until I understood what-- how-- how terrible it was for her, because for her it was everything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, she lost whatever she had but her older sister.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was really her-- actually her child.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she was great enough to-- to send me away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she told me also that the moment it would not be only an emotional thing, but a thing that you really thought through to the end-- you can always come back.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, I never wanted to go back when it was already at that time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But unfortunately, the communists didn't let me in, so I could not meet there any more.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we wrote to each other, and she knew about me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she wrote to my-- she also introduced me to my parents.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, she wrote to my parents what are my-- my possibilities, what I'm good at, and what I could do and what a person I am.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And if I would [INAUDIBLE] I would not-- I would show you the letter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I can't find it at the moment.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
